Interface Collidable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoosterItemObject, DestroyablePlatformObject, EctsItemObject, ItemObject, PlatformObject, ProfessorObject
    public interface Collidable
    Interface for Collidable GameObjects which implements the collide Method for GameObjects, so we can detect the collision for each Object.
